.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, cherry, cucumber, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, camping, rock-climbing, singing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, trance, r&b, country
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, horse, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, snowboarding, swimming
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, pink, red, ebony
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the fan of trance is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person who likes pink##1
 9. the person who likes white is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person eating blueberry is between the person who likes red and the person eating cucumber##2
13. the fan of r&b is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | coffee     | fanta        | iced-tea      |
| Food          | cherry  | cucumber   | blueberry    | radish        |
| Hobby         | camping | singing    | baking       | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | country  | r&b | jazz         | trance       |
| Pet           | lizard  | cat        | fish         | horse         |
| Sport         | sailing | swimming   | snowboarding | climbing      |
| Color     | pink    | white   | ebony        | red        |

